ActDepartment of Agriculture and Agri-Food Act
PrecisAuthority is requested for the Minister of Agriculture and Agri-Food for the purposes of developing, promoting, implementing programs initiatives, activities and projects and to enter into agreements with the government of a Province or Territory or any other organization, including contribution agreements, to implement the Environment component of Growing Forward.
